1146
01:22:13,264 --> 01:22:14,267
[SPEAKER_05]: How has that happened?

1147
01:22:15,445 --> 01:22:17,548
[SPEAKER_07]: Look, I don't commentate on these things.

1148
01:22:17,969 --> 01:22:19,170
[SPEAKER_07]: I don't know if I can avoid it.

1149
01:22:19,230 --> 01:22:19,471
[SPEAKER_05]: Exactly.

1150
01:22:19,591 --> 01:22:20,012
[SPEAKER_07]: Exactly.

1151
01:22:20,132 --> 01:22:21,073
[SPEAKER_07]: You make my point for me.

1152
01:22:21,293 --> 01:22:24,318
[SPEAKER_07]: Look, there's six weeks to go till the general election.

1153
01:22:24,678 --> 01:22:30,046
