1167
01:23:18,297 --> 01:23:20,360
[SPEAKER_07]: And I know this country can be so much better.

1168
01:23:20,841 --> 01:23:22,343
[SPEAKER_07]: And that's what I came into politics for.

1169
01:23:22,683 --> 01:23:24,345
[SPEAKER_07]: And newspapers can write what they like.

1170
01:23:24,365 --> 01:23:26,127
[SPEAKER_07]: The bloke on the tube can say what he likes.

1171
01:23:26,568 --> 01:23:29,452
[SPEAKER_07]: I don't care, because I care about the British people and what happens to them.

1172
01:23:31,214 --> 01:23:37,522
