1179
01:24:03,090 --> 01:24:04,292
[SPEAKER_07]: No, exactly.

1180
01:24:04,812 --> 01:24:07,575
[SPEAKER_07]: You know, look, you need a toughness in this job.

1181
01:24:07,595 --> 01:24:08,396
[SPEAKER_07]: You need a toughness.

1182
01:24:08,596 --> 01:24:11,900
